### Goal
Add the schema foundation live execution builds on, with **zero behavior change to existing consumers**:
1. Optional per-stage `runner` (name-ref OR inline command) + optional run-level `default_runner` in `workflow.yaml`.
2. Optional per-stage `gate` block (`checks` / `seats` | `tier` / `pass_threshold` / `max_rounds` / `abstraction`).
